{"tid":2456710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典(維京佬)算唔算係今年歐國盃其中一大黑馬?","createTime":"2021-03-22T06:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T06:51:39.000Z","uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab001a50ff05ae7d5cc058f30a7fa77fe04f2ae","tid":2456710,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"前中後都係相對成熟嘅一屆<br />\n<br />\n龍門：羅賓奧臣, 踢過羅馬唔多講<br />\n<br />\n中堅：<br />\n連迪洛夫，英超top3中堅，已經打出名堂<br />\n一個都夠守<br />\n<br />\n閘位：<br />\n北歐兵是撚但<br />\n<br />\n中場：<br />\nKulusevski：踢祖記 跟朗哥學野，勁！<br />\n科斯貝治：萊比錫核心，勁！<br />\n<br />\n鋒線：<br />\n雞巴謙莫域：神鋒，當年歐聯小組賽入勁撚多波，今季39歲踢意甲都兩場一球<br />\n伊拉克：黑色E巴，係皇蘇今季勁！<br />\n底褲：潛力新星，羅馬借將，勁！<br />\n<br />\n所以我今屆會支持瑞典！<br />\n有人想睇我分析其他隊會再講。"},{"pid":"60e5b81b969383f763dd80898399ae557e5c0198","tid":2456710,"uid":223337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:41:33.000Z","msg":"OK<br />\nwith thanks"},{"pid":"4ee52bdd2119390465f9f227a93723d013491b54","tid":2456710,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"底乜撚褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d5175b34cb46a923115882da911aee0ff29867","tid":2456710,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"唔井伊布拉希莫維奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e15d5db1f7869b28417b2d84a14c8582252f0c7","tid":2456710,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"伊巴退左啦 懵閪"},{"pid":"3a2504d80c4d8b685863a45d91db796a0bee69a6","tid":2456710,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e15d5db1f7869b28417b2d84a14c8582252f0c7","tid":2456710,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"伊巴退左啦 懵閪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"岩岩先召番